# Keep the build context small: drop host build artifacts, local telemetry
# data, git history, and the GUI's web assets (the container build doesn't
# compile the GUI). Everything else — including SKILL.md, which tael-cli
# embeds via include_str! at compile time — must stay in the context.
.git
target
**/target
data
wal_files
**/*.duckdb
**/*.duckdb.wal
**/node_modules
tael-gui/dist
tael-gui/src-tauri/gen
